title: FSX_P3D PA46 MALIBU MIRAGE 350P HD
description:
Special Features
Original Carenado GNS530 and GNS430 with Reality XP integration option.
Original EMIS (Electronic Module Instrument System)
Cold and Dark start option
Lighting rendering system. Landing, taxi, strobe and beacon
illuminate objects and ground.
Windows lighting scratches effect
Volumetric side view prop effect
Dynamic propeller shines effect.
3D stereo sounds.

Features:
HD quality textures (2048 x2048)
3D gauges
Original HQ digital stereo sounds recorded directly from the real aircraft
Cold and Dark or ready to taxi options for start the simulation.
Customizable panel for controlling windows transparency, instrument reflections and static elements such as wheel chocks and sights props.
Real behavior compared to the real airplane. Real weight and balance. Tested by real pilots.
Realistic night lights effects on panel and cockpit.

**This aircraft does not have a complete 2D panel.


	
Included in the package:
5 HD liveries
1 HD Blank livery
2 models (1 and 2 pilots on board)
PA46 Emergency Checklist PDF
PA46 Normal Procedures PDF
PA46 Performance Tables PDF
PA46 EMIS PDF
Autopilot and AVSS PDF
Weather Radar PDF
Operations Tips and Reality XP Integration PDF
Carenado GNS530 Users Guide PDF
Carenado GNS430 Users Guide PDF
Recommended Settings PDF
